{"tid":1399576,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[地形簡介] 將軍澳區內路線圖","createTime":"2019-08-03T08:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:38:58.000Z","uid":42679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e49d7ece80843df1e536246ff99d0a74669a5d7f","tid":1399576,"uid":42679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"將軍澳即將舉行購物節，策略留翻比各位<br />\n純粹講下平時情況，希望方便到大家入嚟購物<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n宏觀嚟講<br />\n將軍澳由<span style=\"color: red;\">4個小區組成</span>，分別係<span style=\"color: red;\">寶琳、坑口、將軍澳、調景嶺</span>。<br />\n將軍澳外號係「天空之城」，原因係<span style=\"color: red;\">每個小區內所有商場、屋苑幾乎都有天橋連住</span>。<br />\n所有天橋都幾乎係冷氣區。<br />\n整個將軍澳<span style=\"color: red;\">基本上無橫街窄巷</span>街邊小店可言。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GPAeH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GPAeH8.jpg&h=22dec369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小區之間嘅陸路</span></span><br />\n上面提到4個主要分區之間基本上比半行車天橋/馬路截住<br />\n基本上只有幾條行人隧道係可以唔洗經大馬路就去到另一個區。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅線就係意指天橋馬路，而兩旁基本上無行人路。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍箭咀係行人隧道。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxRVZan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxRVZan.jpg&h=230e7e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寶琳區</span></span><br />\n- 基本上所有住宅都有天橋可到<br />\n- 橙框區域之間會有行人路馬路行<br />\n- 商場間都有天橋<br />\n- 山區唔建議入，一無野買、二浪費體力時間、三有村屋<br />\n- 公園個邊多暗角，自己諗<br />\n- 野狗大本型所在地，入夜後購物要小心<br />\n<br />\n交通:<br />\n依賴MTR，將軍澳線總站<br />\n巴士總站係新都城二期地下，地理位置自己睇，可以唔洗諗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8fGUKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8fGUKb.jpg&h=1e68a911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">坑口區</span></span><br />\n- 將軍澳醫院在坑口<br />\n- 巴士總站係MTR上蓋連理街商場地下<br />\n- 但購買人流太多，90%會無車開。<br />\n- 結論都係MTR。<br />\n- 橙框屋邨係無天橋到，只可經地面去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frR3oCR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfrR3oCR.jpg&h=4a31c482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將軍澳區</span></span><br />\n- 主要商場網係紅框區，全部有天橋行到<br />\n- 橙框為無天橋嘅周邊地帶，尚德同富康都有宵夜檔，不過唔知到時有無開<br />\n*****緊記靈實無急症室，位置亦偏僻<br />\n<br />\n近海地帶不建議去，因為多暗角，同埋購物上無戰略意義，離交通又遠。<br />\n如果被逼到過去，盡量留係橙框同海濱長廊(藍線)。<br />\n近海旁個邊都係新樓，應該算係全將軍澳數一數二貴。<br />\n<br />\n交通<br />\n依賴地鐵<br />\n巴士總站在Popcorn，多數經將軍澳隧道出入，但購買人潮下應該用唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DwMbxws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDwMbxws.jpg&h=3fdbd20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">調景嶺</span></span><br />\n基本上對購物而言價值不大<br />\n交通上而言，應該會係唯一一個唔會被封站嘅MTR<br />\n只有紅框部分有天橋。<br />\n維景附近有路去海旁 (藍線)<br />\n巴士站在都會駅地下，但都係經將軍澳隧道走，未必有車出入到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MP5S1pY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMP5S1pY.jpg&h=fa5a3c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小路 - 寶琳入將軍澳</span></span><br />\n由寶琳出發，經寶康公園向行車天橋底行<br />\n過天橋後有巴士車廠，左轉。<br />\n之後得一條主路直去將軍澳尚德同單車館附近。<br />\n始終係小路，行個陣要小心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucKwxwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucKwxwZ.jpg&h=ab190f90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhNicyv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhNicyv.jpg&h=456e09b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不建議的後備路線</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">入康城</span></span><br />\n如被野狗追到就嚟無路可逃，先至好經將軍澳海旁入康城。<br />\n不建議原因：<br />\n1. 路程遠少少，行要20至30分鐘，將軍澳跑入去都最少15分鐘<br />\n2. 大直路，中間無路走，除非跳海<br />\n救護車及任何支援好難入去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kk0qSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kk0qSf.jpg&h=11713294&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36cd7ba6fa892a30e784d6ef7778f69bc899817f","tid":1399576,"uid":42679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:22:58.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"31bbc1c8c559db8cdb2e636727c1c72cb52bb7f4","tid":1399576,"uid":42679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n義士們頂撚住"},{"pid":"78c3b7f8c08f18ae30762228d1cd47fbf2c71b46","tid":1399576,"uid":42679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e461523901226e3ee63f362c04575cc5ed4f39a","tid":1399576,"uid":198314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bd0ac500c6fe66bbe72a8ad1f2abbc1a525afd9","tid":1399576,"uid":198314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"9362705a36c890054894c8c1e088f7432c106421","tid":1399576,"uid":198314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:24:44.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"c7c9284faad7984957eed7035d3166a5ea5c62f5","tid":1399576,"uid":198314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"aeac6e51558da13c